heading: Leviathanâ€™s Maw Dungeon Guide
content: Leviathan's Maw does not have any dangerous monster types, and is a small compact dungeon that requires backtracking. It is solid for farming, but is not currently a possible . There is no boss in this dungeon; once you slay all enemies in the Flooded Ruins, the dungeon is complete. This dungeon unlocks the , a solid defensive aspect for the Rogue. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
